      &lt;p/&gt;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '&lt;div topic=&quot;Summon Nature''s Ally IX&quot; level=&quot;5&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Summon Nature''s Ally IX&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width=&quot;100%&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;2&quot; cellspacing=&quot;2&quot; frame=&quot;VOID&quot; rules=&quot;ROWS&quot;&gt;&lt;tr maxcol=&quot;3&quot; curcol=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;25%&quot;/&gt;&lt;td&gt;Conjuration (Summoning) [See Book]&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr maxcol=&quot;3&quot; curcol=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;25%&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Level:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Druid 9&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr maxcol=&quot;3&quot; curcol=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;25%&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Effect:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;One or more creatures, no two of which can be more than 9 m (30 ft.) apart&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;This spell functions like &lt;i&gt;summon nature''s ally I&lt;/i&gt;,  except that you can summon one 9th-level creature, 1d3 8th-level creatures of the same kind, or 1d4+1 lower-level creatures of the same kind.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;When you use a summoning spell to summon an air, chaotic, earth, evil, fire, good, lawful, or water creature, it is a spell of that type.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p/&gt;&lt;table width=&quot;100%&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;2&quot; cellspacing=&quot;2&quot; frame=&quot;VOID&quot; rules=&quot;ROWS&quot;&gt;

