      &lt;p/&gt;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '&lt;div topic=&quot;Symbol of Stunning&quot; level=&quot;5&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Symbol of Stunning&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width=&quot;100%&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;2&quot; cellspacing=&quot;2&quot; frame=&quot;VOID&quot; rules=&quot;ROWS&quot;&gt;&lt;tr maxcol=&quot;3&quot; curcol=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;25%&quot;/&gt;&lt;td&gt;Enchantment (Compulsion) [Mind-Affecting]&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr maxcol=&quot;3&quot; curcol=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;25%&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Level:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Cleric 7, Sorcerer/Wizard 7&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr maxcol=&quot;3&quot; curcol=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;25%&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Saving Throw:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Will negates&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;This spell functions like &lt;i&gt;symbol of death&lt;/i&gt;, except that all creatures within 60 feet of a &lt;i&gt;symbol of stunning&lt;/i&gt; instead become stunned for 1d6 rounds.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Note:&lt;/i&gt; Magic traps such as &lt;i&gt;symbol of stunning&lt;/i&gt; are hard to detect and disable. A rogue (only) can use the Search skill to find a &lt;i&gt;symbol of stunning&lt;/i&gt; and Disable Device to thwart it. The DC in each case is 25 + spell level, or 32 for &lt;i&gt;symbol of stunning&lt;/i&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Material Component:&lt;/i&gt; Mercury and phosphorus, plus powdered diamond and opal with a total value of at least 5,000 gp.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p/&gt;
